==派生作品==
[[西藏与喜马拉雅图书馆|西藏与喜马拉雅图书馆]]复刻了Jomolhari字体，为[[Adobe_InDesign|Adobe InDesign]] CS3及CS4创造出Jomolhari ID字体。该字体添加了附加的lookup以及通用OpenType特性以使文字能在这些版本中正确显示。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thlib.org/tools/#wiki=/access/wiki/site/26a34146-33a6-48ce-001e-f16ce7908a6a/jomolhari%20id.html |title=Jomolhari ID |website=The Tibetan and Himalayan Library |accessdate=30 March 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110005635/http://www.thlib.org/tools/#wiki=/access/wiki/site/26a34146-33a6-48ce-001e-f16ce7908a6a/jomolhari%20id.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitaltibetan.org/index.php/Tibetan_Fonts |title=Tibetan Fonts |website=Digital Tibetan |accessdate=12 April 2019 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221134631/http://www.digitaltibetan.org/index.php/Tibetan_Fonts |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[魏安|魏安]]也创造了该字体的复刻版BabelStone Tibetan以提供扩展支持。该字体添加后来的Unicode版本中收录的藏文字符，添加了更多的字符组合，尤其是用于藏文速记缩写和转写西夏语的组合。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.babelstone.co.uk/Fonts/Tibetan.html |title=BabelStone Fonts: BabelStone Tibetan |author=Andrew West |website=BabelStone |accessdate=18 June 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108233835/https://www.babelstone.co.uk/Fonts/Tibetan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

